    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and carpet. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but it may require some upcoming maintenance, such as a suspension refresh or addressing a minor oil seep. It is a solid option for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections and minor repairs.",
