    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$34,500 - Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience. It's clean, dependable, and ready for its next adventure\u2014a perfect choice for anyone looking for a quality car that's been treated with respect!",
      "price": 34500.0,
